title: Veg Stall at Chiang Mai Gate
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Thai, Fast food, Take-out
description: Food cart alongside with other carts just inside Chiang Mai Gate at  front of the Chiang Mai Gate Market. No name on the cart so look for the yellow and red Thai signs in the front (means vegetarian). Feb 2015 reported also using egg.
